l\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Intel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Intel\"}, {\"begin\": 2301, \"end\": 2304, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/OBS_Studio\", \"score\": 0.9999950485584834, \"rank\": 4.951465892506799e-06, \"text\": \"OBS\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/OBS_Studio\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/OBS_Studio\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The industry partnership\", \"from\": 2196, \"to\": 2220}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Winter Games Beijing\", \"from\": 2233, \"to\": 2265}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Our goal at the Olympic Games Paris 2024 is a step closer toward making 8K mainstream, and to deliver live 8K streaming using advanced h.266/VVC encoding technologies that reach the highest quality at the lowest bitrate possible around the globe,\\\" says Ravindra (Ravi) Velhal, global content technology strategist and 8K lead in the Software and Advanced Technology Group at Intel.\", \"from\": 2388, \"to\": 2770, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2530, \"end\": 2533, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Versatile_Video_Coding\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5122882514342728e-18, \"text\": \"VVC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Versatile_Video_Coding\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Versatile_Video_Coding\"}, {\"begin\": 2652, \"end\": 2656, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunday\", \"score\": 0.9884733448470956, \"rank\": 0.011657783254988506, \"text\": \"Ravi\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunday\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunday\"}, {\"begin\": 2735, \"end\": 2760, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novell\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.776057505688643e-19, \"text\": \"Advanced Technology Group\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://