821, \"to\": 2857}, {\"ngram\": \"end\", \"from\": 2871, \"to\": 2874}, {\"ngram\": \"Xeon CPUs\", \"from\": 2933, \"to\": 2942}, {\"ngram\": \"encode and Intel-based client CPUs\", \"from\": 2946, \"to\": 2980}, {\"ngram\": \"Arc GPUs\", \"from\": 2985, \"to\": 2993}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It provides a pathway for the future of low-latency, broadcast-grade 8K livestreaming over the internet.\", \"from\": 3006, \"to\": 3110, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a pathway\", \"from\": 3018, \"to\": 3027}, {\"ngram\": \"the future\", \"from\": 3032, \"to\": 3042}, {\"ngram\": \"low-latency\", \"from\": 3046, \"to\": 3057}, {\"ngram\": \"broadcast-grade 8K\", \"from\": 3059, \"to\": 3077}, {\"ngram\": \"the internet\", \"from\": 3097, \"to\": 3109}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That process of getting 8K live content from the Olympic Games stadium in Paris to an 8K-enabled TV on the other side of the planet is highly complex.\", \"from\": 3112, \"to\": 3262, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3186, \"end\": 3191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999958595254, \"rank\": 4.14036104137061e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That process\", \"from\": 3112, \"to\": 3124}, {\"ngram\": \"8K live content\", \"from\": 3136, \"to\": 3151}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games stadium\", \"from\": 3157, \"to\": 3182}, {\"ngram\": \"an 8K-enabled TV\", \"from\": 3195, \"to\": 3211}, {\"ngram\": \"the other side\", \"from\": 3215, \"to\": 3229}, {\"ngram\": \"the planet\", \"from\": 3233, \"to\": 3243}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's enabled by a constellation of Intel hardware and software technologies.\", \"from\": 3263, \"to\": 3339, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3298, \"end\": 3303, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Intel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4471321806915276e-17, \"text\": \"Intel\", \"types\": [\