akes about seven to 10 years for the media industry to evolve and embrace the next standard of visual and audio technology, says Velhal, citing examples of tectonic shifts in the evolution of the global media industry: 8K display technology introduces a much stronger sensation of realism, thanks to its ability to fully immerse the viewer in rich visual and audio content, a higher dynamic range and a higher frame rate.\", \"from\": 3866, \"to\": 4304, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"about seven to 10 years\", \"from\": 3887, \"to\": 3910}, {\"ngram\": \"the media industry\", \"from\": 3915, \"to\": 3933}, {\"ngram\": \"the next standard\", \"from\": 3956, \"to\": 3973}, {\"ngram\": \"visual and audio technology\", \"from\": 3977, \"to\": 4004}, {\"ngram\": \"Velhal\", \"from\": 4011, \"to\": 4017}, {\"ngram\": \"examples\", \"from\": 4026, \"to\": 4034}, {\"ngram\": \"tectonic shifts\", \"from\": 4038, \"to\": 4053}, {\"ngram\": \"the evolution\", \"from\": 4057, \"to\": 4070}, {\"ngram\": \"the global media industry\", \"from\": 4074, \"to\": 4099}, {\"ngram\": \"8K display technology\", \"from\": 4101, \"to\": 4122}, {\"ngram\": \"a much stronger sensation\", \"from\": 4134, \"to\": 4159}, {\"ngram\": \"realism\", \"from\": 4163, \"to\": 4170}, {\"ngram\": \"its ability\", \"from\": 4182, \"to\": 4193}, {\"ngram\": \"the viewer\", \"from\": 4211, \"to\": 4221}, {\"ngram\": \"rich visual and audio content\", \"from\": 4225, \"to\": 4254}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Capturing rich, immersive 8K content may sound like a complex job, but getting it to where it needs to be - on the screens of viewers across the planet - is more difficult.\", \"from\": 4306, \"to\": 4478, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"8K content\", \"from\": 4332, \"to\": 4342}, {\"ngram\": \"a complex job\", \"from\": 4358, \"to\": 4371}, {\"ngram\": \"the screens\", \"from\": 4417, \"to\": 4428}, {\"ngram\": \"viewers\", \"from\": 4432, \"to\": 4439}, {\"ngram\": \"the planet\", \"from\": 4447, \"to\": 4457}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During the Olympic Games Paris 2024, Ravi and his team will work on several events acquiring, processing and streaming petabytes of data.\", \"from\": 4480, \"to\": 4617, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4517, \"end\": 4521, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunday\", \"score\": 0.9884733448470956, \"rank\": 0.011657783254988506, \"text\": \"Ravi\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunday\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunday\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games Paris\", \"from\": 4487, \"to\": 4510}, {\"ngram\": \"his team\", \"from\": 4526, \"to\": 4534}, {\"ngram\": \"several events\", \"from\": 4548, \"to\": 4562}, {\"ngram\": \"petabytes\", \"from\": 4599, \"to\": 4608}, {\"ngram\": \"data\", \"from\": 4612, \"to\": 4616}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a job suited for a collection of advanced Intel-based AI platform technologies like Intel Advanced Matrix Extensions (AMX) AI accelerators and Intel Deep Learning (DL) Boost that enable complex AI workloads to run without increasing the overall computing footprint.\", \"from\": 4619, \"to\": 4890, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4678, \"end\": 4680, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AI_accelerator\", \"score\": 0.8997705369182605, \"rank\": 0.11139447111127547, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AI_accelerator\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AI_accelerator\"}, {\"begin\": 4819, \"end\": 4821, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AI_accelerator\", \"score\": 0.8997705369182605, \"rank\": 0.11139447111127547, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AI_accelerator\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AI_accelerator\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a job\", \"from\": 4624, \"to\": 4629}, {\"ngram\": \"a collection\", \"from\": 4641, \"to\": 4653}, {\"ngram\": \"Intel Advanced Matrix Extensions (AMX) AI 